    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Upright stands, typically resembling drying racks, with projecting arms or cross bars used to hold clothing in a dressing room or bedroom. The rack is designed so that clothing may be folded across the arms or bars. Pegs may also be included for hanging clothes.</Note_Text>
